Flow control and Logical Operators
if, else, elif

if condition:
  do this
else:
  do this

  > greater than
  < less than
  >= greater than or equal to 
  <= less than or equal to
  == equal to 
  != Not equal to 

  Modulo % 

  modulo gives you the remainder of division

  7 % 2 = 2+2+2+1
  2 can be divided into 7: 3 times with a remainder of 1 = 2+2+2+1
  7 % 2 would output 1 

Nested if statements checks from top down if conditions are true and moves down accordingly.

if condition:
  if another condition:
    do this
    else:
      do this
     
else:
 do this

if condition1:
  do a

elif condition2:
    do b 
else:
  do c

And statements &

if condition1 & condition2 & condition3:
  do this

else:
  do this